item.title: Welcome! - Karibu!
item.description: Welcome to Nairobi! After a long, pleasant flight we arrived at Jomo Kenyatta Airport in Nairobi. My wife Dorothee and I enjoyed the flight, and even Lucy, the cat, arrived in good condition, albeit not amused.
